irst time, this study attempts to offer a useful approach to the micro\nfoundations of affective polarization, and the results guide us how to avoid\nthe dilemmas from this polarization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2023 07:48:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-27"}
