 over 20\\% in retrieval accuracy\nand almost reduces over 80\\% training time when new data arrives continuously.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2023 07:56:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-27"}
